### <i class='icon-sitemap'></i> Static

Generates a **self-contained static website**, i.e. all generated links are relative and no server
is needed for viewing the website!
</div>

<div class="large-4 columns" markdown="1">
### <i class='icon-plus'></i> Any Markup

**HTML**, **Haml**, **ERB**, **CSS**, **Sass**, **Markdown**, **Textile**, **RDoc**, ... -- use the
[markup/template engine/CSS language](documentation/reference/extensions/content_processor/) *you* like!
</div>

<div class="large-4 columns" markdown="1">
### <i class='icon-check'></i> Built-in Helpers

With tools to **automatically generate** [menus], [breadcrumb trails], [news feeds] and more, you can
concentrate on writing content!

[menus]: documentation/reference/extensions/tag/menu.html
[breadcrumb trails]: documentation/reference/extensions/tag/breadcrumb_trail.html
[news feeds]: documentation/reference/extensions/path_handler/feed.html
