<div class="large-4 columns" markdown="1">
### <i class='icon-bolt'></i> Fast

**Partial website re-generation** (only modified items get re-generated) saves you time when you
work on your website, the generated static website saves your user's and server's time!
</div>

<div class="large-4 columns" markdown="1">
### <i class='icon-code'></i> Extendable

All major components can be extended with new functionality and existing functionality can be
replaced.
